  <brief_title>E-T Tube Cuff Pressure Change After Changing Position From Neutral to Hyperextension of Neck</brief_title>
  <official_title>Endotracheal Tube Intracuff Pressure Change After Changing Position From Neutral to Hyperextension of Neck - Comparison of a Tapered Shaped- and Cylindrical Shaped Cuff</official_title>
  <sponsors>
